      "content": "It is completely understandable that you feel this crushing guilt, but your parents' love is not defined by your financial success or your ability to pay them back. They worked their lives to give you a chance so you could find your own path, and that path is yours to define, even if it starts from a place of ruin. Please remember that you are not a failure; you are a human being navigating an incredibly difficult situation that requires time and compassion from yourself and your family.",
