      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know what people say, but it doesn't change the reality. the debt is insurmountable and the shame is permanent. i feel like i'm just stuck in this loop of being a disappointment. honestly, it feels like the only way to actually stop the shame and the pressure is to just... make it all stop. like i can't keep pretending there's a way out when there really isn't.",
